<figureCitation box="[1203,1248,439,465]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1318,1342]" captionTargetBox="[152,1434,182,1293]" captionTargetId="figure-27@5.[151,1435,181,1294]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Myrmecina bawai sp. nov. worker, holotype; A) Clypeus and mandibles; B) Mesosoma in dorsal view; C) Denticle on propodeal dorsum, propodeal spine, petiole and postpetiole in profile view; D) First gastral tergum in dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4982576" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4982576/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="164">3 C</figureCitation>
